{"tid":1790720,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教育局稱至今有80名老師被捕","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T08:08:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"130fe4ceebb466222f2c9a96f31e3dd3726f43ca","tid":1790720,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: NOW ALERT"},{"pid":"3fd378b476781390b557692ac1c177805ed4bec4","tid":1790720,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:05:27.000Z","msg":"教育局指老師若涉嚴重刑事罪行，即使未宣判按現行法例亦可停職"},{"pid":"f8f48c815dfb7ed4189d28b5ec3d2eabd8f0f54c","tid":1790720,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撐暴政有 其他人一蓋消滅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人報仇"},{"pid":"428f15182e43d56a27180022bef5b26e963f4aa7","tid":1790720,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Y6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=eb235ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"e35ea9f40920bea6b2ec1bfb4720363c919578ca","tid":1790720,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"清算已經來臨"},{"pid":"f47627969775d76b9fae7bc072cc2468ade1c039","tid":1790720,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"至今有123宗教師有關的教師專業操守投訴，大部份涉及散播仇恨言論、挑釁行為及發布不當教材。楊指，教育局已有13宗完成處分，包括發出5封警告信、7封勸喻信、另有1名官校教師涉及使用不當教材，已被停職調查。此外，有30宗個案不成立，31宗屬可能成立，正待教師回覆。<br />\n<br />\n80位教師及教學助理被捕 若學校處理有偏離 會逐一跟進<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，目前已有近千名18歲以下學生被捕，80位教師及教學助理被捕，今日已致函學校，提供涉及違法教師及違規學生提供指引，若學校處理有所偏離，將會逐一跟進。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，大部份老師在這段期間均盡忠職守，只是「少部份害群之馬，令學界蒙羞。」他指，若違反專業操專的教師個案嚴重，會採取可行措施，並指《資助則例》，教師若涉及刑事或不當行為，學校可著令教師停職，以保障學生安全，維持學校正常運作，強調「唔係未審先判」，又強調，教育局在現有處理投訴個案程序，會讓涉事教師有充份申述同自辨機會。"}]}